Hardware:

+ SFE Red Board (https://www.sparkfun.com/products/13293)
+ HamShield (http://hamshield.com/) with RDA1846 RF TXR (2m, 1.25m, 70cm)
+ SFE button shield (https://www.sparkfun.com/products/13293)

Pins:

 A0: LCD shield buttons
 A1: nCS for the RDA1846
 A2: analog input from HamShield
 A3: RST for RDA1846
 A4: DAT for RDA1846
 A5: CLK for RDA1846
 D0:
 D1:
 D2: 
 D3:
 D4: LCD bit 4
 D5: LCD bit 5
 D6: LCD bit 6
 D7: LCD bit 7
 D8: LCD RS
 D9: LCD enable
D10: LCD backlight brightness adjust
D11:
D12:
D13:
D14:
D15:
